		<div>I also have a problem with the spell drops of OoW. The issue of 'perma-camped' mobs, players farming for RL cash, or whatever, really cheeses me off.<br />
 <br />
I have joined WoS groups, seen runes drops (1), and saw it go to a WARRIOR who ALREADY had all of his discs! Why? JUST because he rolled high! The ONLY thing he could do with it was sell it. HE HAD HIS 'SPELLS' ALREADY!<br />
